text: Jens Teunckens (born 30 January 1998) is a Belgian professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for AEK Larnaca. ==Club career== A youth product of Club Brugge, Teunckens joined Antwerp on loan in 2018, and joined Antwerp permanently when the loan ended. Teunckens made his professional debut for Antwerp in a 2-1 Belgian First Division A win over K.A.S. Eupen on 9 May 2019. ==International career== Teunckens was called up by the senior Belgium squad in October 2019 for a UEFA Euro 2020 qualifier against Kazakhstan. ==References== ==External links== * BelgianFootball Profile * Royal Antwerp Profile Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:People from Geel Category:Belgian footballers Category:Belgium youth international footballers Category:Royal Antwerp F.C. players Category:Club Brugge KV players Category:Belgian First Division A players Category:Association football goalkeepers
